      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat(web-search): add SerpApi plugin with web search provider and 25+ specialized tools",
        "body": "Add SerpApi plugin with web search provider and 31 specialized tools\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\n\r\n- OpenClaw had no SerpApi integration — agents could not use SerpApi's 100+ search engines or its specialized search verticals (flights, hotels, shopping, maps, YouTube, scholar, finance, news, etc.).\r\n- Adds a new `serpapi` plugin that registers as a `web_search` provider (display name: **SerpApi Search**) and exposes 31 dedicated tools covering Google, Bing, DuckDuckGo, Yahoo, YouTube, Maps, Scholar, Finance, Flights, Hotels, Shopping, News, Events, Jobs, Amazon, eBay, Walmart, Tripadvisor, Trends, Autocomplete, Lens, AI Overview, Facebook/Instagram profiles, and Weather.\r\n- Plugin id: `serpapi`; config: `plugins.entries.serpapi.*`; API key: `webSearch.apiKey` config or `SERPAPI_API_KEY` env var.\r\n- Cache, timeout, language, and result count are configurable via plugin config.\r\n- No changes to core or other plugins; uses existing `provider-web-search` SDK helpers.\r\n\r\n### Tools\r\n\r\n| Tool | Description |\r\n|---|---|\r\n| `serpapi_ai_overview` | Fetch the full Google AI Overview for a search using a page_token |\r\n| `serpapi_amazon` | Search Amazon for products — titles, prices, ratings, Prime status, ASIN |\r\n| `serpapi_amazon_product` | Fetch detailed Amazon product info by ASIN |\r\n| `serpapi_autocomplete` | Google search autocomplete suggestions for a partial query |\r\n| `serpapi_bing` | Web search via Bing — titles, URLs, snippets |\r\n| `serpapi_duckduckgo` | Web search via DuckDuckGo — organic results, knowledge graph, news |\r\n| `serpapi_ebay` | Search eBay listings — titles, prices, conditions, links |\r\n| `serpapi_ebay_product` | Detailed eBay product info by product ID |\r\n| `serpapi_events` | Google Events search — title, date, address, ticket links |\r\n| `serpapi_facebook_profile` | Fetch a public Facebook profile |\r\n| `serpapi_finance` | Stock prices, currency rates, and crypto via Google Finance |\r\n| `serpapi_flights` | Real flight prices and itineraries via Google Flights |\r\n| `serpapi_hotels` | Hotels and accommodation via Google Hotels — price, rating, amenities |\r\n| `serpapi_immersive_product` | Detailed Google product info by page_token from Shopping results |\r\n| `serpapi_instagram_profile` | Fetch a public Instagram profile |\r\n| `serpapi_jobs` | Google Jobs search — titles, companies, locations, salary |\r\n| `serpapi_lens` | Google Lens reverse image search |\r\n| `serpapi_maps` | Local businesses, restaurants, POIs via Google Maps |\r\n| `serpapi_maps_reviews` | Reviews for a place on Google Maps |\r\n| `serpapi_news` | Recent articles via Google News — headlines, sources, dates, URLs |\r\n| `serpapi_scholar` | Academic papers, research articles, and citations via Google Scholar |\r\n| `serpapi_shopping` | Google Shopping — product names, prices, stores, ratings |\r\n| `serpapi_tripadvisor` | Destinations, hotels, restaurants, and attractions via Tripadvisor |\r\n| `serpapi_trends` | Google Trends — interest over time, by region, related topics/queries |\r\n| `serpapi_walmart` | Walmart product listings — titles, prices, ratings, links |\r\n| `serpapi_walmart_product` | Detailed Walmart product info by product ID |\r\n| `serpapi_weather` | Current weather or forecast for a location via Google |\r\n| `serpapi_yahoo` | Web search via Yahoo! — titles, URLs, snippets |\r\n| `serpapi_youtube` | YouTube search — videos, channels, shorts with metadata |\r\n| `serpapi_youtube_transcript` | Fetch the transcript of a YouTube video |\r\n| `serpapi_youtube_video` | YouTube video metadata — title, description, channel, views, chapters |\r\n\r\n## Real behavior proof\r\n\r\n- Behavior addressed: no SerpApi integration existed; this PR adds the full plugin.\r\n- Real environment tested: local OpenClaw checkout on macOS.\r\n- Exact steps or command run after this patch: `pnpm test extensions/serpapi`\r\n- Evidence after fix:\r\n  ```\r\n   ✓  extensions/serpapi/src/serpapi-client.test.ts (11 tests) 53ms\r\n   ✓  extensions/serpapi/src/serpapi-search-provider.test.ts (7 tests) 248ms\r\n\r\n   Test Files  2 passed (2)\r\n        Tests  18 passed (18)\r\n     Duration  590ms\r\n  ```\r\n- Observed result after fix: all 18 tests pass across the client and web search provider.\r\n- What was not tested: full cross-platform validation, automated CI live API calls.\r\n- Proof limitations: automated CI live API calls not run; live behavior validated manually via Docker with a real SerpApi key.\r\n\r\n## Tests and validation\r\n\r\n- Added `serpapi-client.test.ts` — HTTP client, error handling, cache behavior, missing-key error.\r\n- Added `serpapi-search-provider.test.ts` — provider registration, credential path, and config application.\r\n- New plugin addition; no prior behavior to regress against.\r\n\r\n## Risk checklist\r\n\r\n- [x] User-visible behavior changed — new plugin, tools, and web search provider available when enabled.\r\n- [x] Config/environment changed — new `plugins.entries.serpapi.*`; new `SERPAPI_API_KEY` env var.\r\n- [x] Security/auth/network changed — new outbound HTTPS to `serpapi.com`, gated behind API key; key never logged.\r\n- [ ] Breaking change to existing behavior — no existing behavior affected.\r\n\r\n",
